title: cgpsmapper_cracked.commercial.routable.v0.92_191
description:
This programme allows you to make your own custom Garmin compatible maps - the commercial version (which is VERY expensive) allows to do do a whole bunch of things like routable maps, and indexing - which the free version does not.

This is rather old version - I've upped it because it was nearly impossible to find it - I thought for the enthusiasts, it would be nice to have it up here as well.  Thanks to whoever was the first to upload it, and to 'LAKER' who cracked it.

This is a plea, request to anybody with the required skills - is there a keygen out there?  Or a much later cracked version?  It's already on  version 0.98...

I would be eternally greatful if someone could upload the above.

P.S. - I've made quite a number of maps with this, including perfectly working routable ones - works perfectly.

Have fun!
